## 3.0.8 (2026-6-13)

### New feature:

-   Support minimizing and restoring the translation window from the macOS Dock.
-   Add standard macOS window controls for the Apple Silicon build.

### Bugs fixed:

-   Improve selected-text translation on macOS without relying on osascript.

